<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('../includes/head.ejs') %>
    <style>
        .hero-section { position: relative; padding: 150px 0; background-color: #f0fdfa; overflow: hidden; text-align: center; }
        .hero-background { position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 150%; height: 25%; border-top-left-radius: 50%; border-top-right-radius: 50%; background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #0d9488, #22d3ee); }
        .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 10; }
        .hero-image { max-width: 220px; transition: transform 0.3s ease; }
        .hero-image:hover { transform: scale(1.05) rotate(3deg); }
        .systems-section { padding: 80px 0; background-color: #ffffff; }
        .system-card { border: none; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0,0,0,0.1), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease; }
        .system-card:hover { transform: translateY(-10px); box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1), 0 10px 10px -5px rgba(0,0,0,0.04); }
        .system-card img { height: 128px; width: auto; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        .text-teal { color: #0d9488; }
        .btn-orange { background-color: #fb923c; border-color: #fb923c; color: white; transition: all 0.2s; }
        .btn-orange:hover { background-color: #f97316; border-color: #f97316; color: white; transform: scale(1.1); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../includes/tbcare/navbar-landing.ejs') %>

    <section class="hero-section">
        <div class="hero-background"></div>
        <div class="container hero-content">
            <div class="row align-items-center justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-lg-3 d-none d-lg-block wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-delay="0.4s">
                    <img src="/images/tbcare_landing/monster.png" alt="Monster Illustration" class="img-fluid hero-image">
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-10 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.2s">
                    <h1 class="display-4 font-weight-bold text-teal">Know Your Cough,<br>Get The Right Treatment</h1>
                    <p class="lead text-secondary mt-3">Sistem pintar untuk mendeteksi potensi TBC dari suara batuk, membantu pasien & dokter mendapatkan solusi lebih cepat dan tepat.</p>
                    <a href="/login" class="btn btn-orange btn-lg rounded-pill mt-4 px-5">Log In</a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-3 d-none d-lg-block wow fadeInRight" data-wow-delay="0.4s">
                    <img src="/images/tbcare_landing/device.png" alt="Device Illustration" class="img-fluid hero-image">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="scroll-banner-container">
        <div class="scroll-banner-content"></div>
    </div>
    
    <section class="systems-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12 text-center mb-5 wow fadeInDown">
                    <h2 class="font-weight-bold text-teal">Our Systems</h2>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.2s">
                    <div class="card system-card p-4 text-center h-100">
                        <img src="/images/tbcare_landing/device/Hardware.png" alt="Hardware" class="mx-auto">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h4 class="card-title text-teal font-weight-bold">Hardware</h4>
                            <p class="card-text text-secondary">Perangkat khusus untuk merekam suara batuk dengan sensor audio sensitivitas tinggi.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.4s">
                    <div class="card system-card p-4 text-center h-100">
                        <img src="/images/tbcare_landing/device/Web.png" alt="Web Dashboard" class="mx-auto">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h4 class="card-title text-teal font-weight-bold">Web</h4>
                            <p class="card-text text-secondary">Platform web untuk dokter mengelola data pasien dan melihat hasil analisis secara real-time.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.6s">
                    <div class="card system-card p-4 text-center h-100">
                        <img src="/images/tbcare_landing/device/mobile.png" alt="Mobile App" class="mx-auto">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h4 class="card-title text-teal font-weight-bold">Mobile App</h4>
                            <p class="card-text text-secondary">Aplikasi mobile untuk pasien melakukan self-check dan mengunggah rekaman batuk.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('../includes/tbcare/footer-landing.ejs') %>
    <%- include('../includes/end.ejs') %>
</body>
</html>